Project description

This is the package for Pyston "lite", the JIT part of Pyston,a faster implementation of Python. Pyston lite does not contain all of theoptimizations of full Pyston, but it is still 10-25% faster on many workloads.

Pyston lite is currently only available for Python 3.7-3.10
